NUMBER 1908
NAME Palace, East Courtyard
DAY_LIGHT
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
This newly sculpted courtyard is a masterpiece of creative stonework and
gardening. Slabs of slate and flagstone cover this round expanse between
the gates and the palace. Surrounding the stone are neatly trimmed bushes
and trees.
*DESCRIPTION_END
